sequenceDiagram
    actor Candidate
    participant UI as Web Client (React)
    participant API as Flask REST API
    participant AI as AI Monitoring Engine
    participant RSE as Risk-Scoring Engine
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant NS as Notification Service
    actor Recruiter

    Candidate->>UI: Log in and start assessment
    UI->>API: Authenticate (JWT + MFA)
    API->>DB: Validate credentials
    API-->>UI: Token + session created
    UI->>AI: Stream webcam frames + browser events
    loop During assessment
        AI->>AI: Verify identity, detect phone, track gaze/head pose, monitor tab
        AI->>API: Post integrity event
        API->>DB: Persist integrity event (+ evidence)
        API->>RSE: Update risk score
        RSE-->>API: Updated risk score + breakdown
        alt Risk >= threshold
            API->>NS: Raise alert
            NS->>Recruiter: In-app + Email + SMS alert
        end
    end
    Candidate->>UI: Submit assessment
    UI->>API: Finalize session
    API->>RSE: Compute final risk score
    API->>DB: Store score + report
    API-->>Recruiter: Integrity report available
